# Martenweave frontend prototype — environment variables
#
# This local prototype does not require any runtime environment variables.
# It loads demo data from src/data.js and runs entirely in the browser.
# No API keys, secrets, or backend endpoints are configured by default.
#
# If you later connect this prototype to a local Martenweave API, you can
# uncomment and set variables here, for example:
# VITE_MODELOPS_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
